    "description": "欢迎游玩《荒野战纪》，这是一款结合战棋与轻度Rogue的策略角色扮演游戏，游戏改编自风靡欧美的同名桌游。在游戏中，你可以感受战略与荒野风情的完美结合，深入活灵活现的动物族群，体验英雄故事与多彩的冒险史诗。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/e91f1e704415d0ab97d992c0894898a9.poster.avif?t=1724050070\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/e91f1e704415d0ab97d992c0894898a9.webm?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>游戏的每个章节都是一段风格各异的冒险之旅。在随机生成的的2D手绘地图世界中，沉浸于引人入胜的故事情节，升级培养你的战术小队，为每个英雄装备独特的符文和能力，激发他们的潜能。探索隐藏的宝藏，解锁更多新角色，获取各种威力强大的符文和升级选项，书写独属于你的荒野战纪。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/7c2509f58992b8e4e52754ea7f0707dd.avif?t=1724050070\" width=618 height=120 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索充满活力的世界</h2>精美的手绘2D画面为《荒野战纪》的奇妙世界注入了生动的活力。在游戏中，你将与一系列可爱的拟人动物盟友或对手相遇，每个角色都独具魅力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/6d6a0cb94a30ad03608889f7d45690fa.poster.avif?t=1724050070\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/6d6a0cb94a30ad03608889f7d45690fa.webm?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/6d6a0cb94a30ad03608889f7d45690fa.mp4?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的战棋策略玩法</h2>探索不同战斗策略、复杂技能组合以及有趣的角色养成。巧妙地操控地图环境，引诱你的敌人陷入尖刺陷阱或有毒淤泥的险境。拥抱神秘的神龛之力，善用周遭环境，逆转战局！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/b1bf69cb64c94f1002bf00eee667020d.poster.avif?t=1724050070\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/b1bf69cb64c94f1002bf00eee667020d.webm?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/b1bf69cb64c94f1002bf00eee667020d.mp4?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引人入胜的故事</h2>与灰衣一同踏上这趟非凡之旅，与一班多姿多彩的动物角色相遇，它们将成为你坚定的朋友，亦或是可怕的对手。帮助灰衣夺回失去的荣誉，直面潜伏在荒野中的无数威胁，在这片奇妙新世界中开创自己的天地。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/d68586d1fe9155c454b9784c390bf210.poster.avif?t=1724050070\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/d68586d1fe9155c454b9784c390bf210.webm?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/d68586d1fe9155c454b9784c390bf210.mp4?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与敌人交涉</h2>通过“和谈”功能，在战斗中以特殊方式与对手互动。释放可以改变战局的特殊效果，让你的对手在恐惧中颤抖吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/3ece0522fded98a4fb7d425c8e4737cd.poster.avif?t=1724050070\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/3ece0522fded98a4fb7d425c8e4737cd.webm?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/3ece0522fded98a4fb7d425c8e4737cd.mp4?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高度可重复游玩性</h2>随机生成的世界地图和丰富多样的游戏事件为游戏带来了极高的可重复性，简化后的机制则迎合了喜欢挑战不同难度的玩家。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/485e24f1ae8067946586ce5720c769df.poster.avif?t=1724050070\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/485e24f1ae8067946586ce5720c769df.webm?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1538900/extras/485e24f1ae8067946586ce5720c769df.mp4?t=1724050070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
